overview:
IT-Netlogistics provides nationwide information technology (IT) and communication network services.

We have designed our IT services and processes over the past 30 years in response to our clients’ ever-changing needs. IT-Netlogistics provides:

• Technology rollout management • Voice and data system installations • WiFi installation and wireless networks • Structured cabling • IT break/fix services with onsite IT technical repair • IT hardware and software integration services • Network monitoring services, including technical dispatch • New office IT Installations • Installation and support services for point of sale (POS) equipment • Disaster recovery support services • IT help desk and IT dispatch center

IT-Netlogistics delivers a wide range of telecommunications and networking services to enterprise clients, as well as small and mid-sized companies.

We can provide total IT support or augment existing platforms, allowing internal staff to concentrate on more crucial issues. IT-Netlogistics is committed to service excellence and offers a cost-effective solution for any size company.
